description:
Minecraft Server. The new Minecraft 1.16 Nether Update has hit with a big ground shaking impact! Today we finish up the exterior of Shade-E-E's and then head to the new nether with Wels and Keralis to do some initial exploring. Then we get to farming fungi, bartering gold, and blasting netherite.
